"{\"uid\": \"news18.com-viral-woman-grabs-and-kisses-tom-cruise-at-paris-olympics-closing-ceremony-internet-unhappy-9012717.html\", \"text\": \"Engaging in a little risky business, Tom Cruise gave a flying closure to the 2024 Paris Olympics before handing it off to Los Angeles for the 2028 Games. Bringing his usual cinematic flair, Cruise was seen performing a dramatic stunt from the roof of the Stade de France, leaving the crowd amazed. However, in a sudden turn of events, the actor had an unexpected encounter when a woman grabbed and kissed him while recording the entire thing on camera.  Footage of the woman's act has been going viral, leaving fans divided over it. Notably, this happened after the Hollywood actor came down from the top of the stadium to the tunes of the Mission: Impossible theme. As he started greeting fans, one of them grabbed him and kissed him on the cheek.  How'd that lady almost make out with Tom Cruise on international TV \\ud83d\\ude02#ClosingCeremonypic.twitter.com/IxtmIUPdcA- Georgia Rose \\ud83c\\uddff\\ud83c\\udde6 \\ud83c\\udf49 (@Rasheeda_S)August 11, 2024  The video stirred controversy online, with many calling it inappropriate. Some also pointed out how the internet would have reacted if the roles were reversed in this incident.  A user wrote, \\\"Damn she just risked it all.\\\"  Damn she just risked it all. \\ud83e\\udd23\\ud83e\\udd23.- Mr.Backlogged Gamer (@backloggedgamr)August 11, 2024  Another commented, \\\"Imagine if the roles were reversed.\\\"  Imagine if the roles were reversed\\u2026- ham (@meme_cycle)August 11, 2024  \\\"There was a bit of a misunderstanding. Recently, Lady Gaga and Tom Cruise shared a friendly hug at the Paris Olympics while attending the women's gymnastics event. This moment was captured on camera and might have been misinterpreted by some viewers,\\\" a comment read.  there was a bit of a misunderstanding. Recently, Lady Gaga and Tom Cruise shared a friendly hug at the Paris Olympics while attending the women's gymnastics event\\u00b9. This moment was captured on camera and might have been misinterpreted by some viewers.- tayyaba (@tayyaba_fatima2)August 11, 2024  One of the individuals noted, \\\"Cringe. If a man did that to a female celebrity there would be questions.\\\"  Cringe.  \\ud83d\\ude33If a man did that to a female celebrity there would be questions\\u2026- \\ud83d\\udc95 Dewy \\u2640\\ufe0f (@BlueSkiesG1)August 11, 2024  A person also stated, \\\"The worst kind of people in the audience. Absolute zero respect for personal space. If it had been a man with a woman, people would already be looking for all his information to burn him alive.\\\"  The worst kind of people in audiences. Absolute zero respect for personal space. If it had been a man with a woman people would already be looking for all his information to burn him alive.- Siul Oczoro \\ud83c\\udf9f\\ud83c\\udfa7\\ud83c\\udfac\\ud83d\\udcbf\\ud83d\\udcd8 (@SiulOczoro989)August 11, 2024  Swipe Left For Next Video  The incident came amid the dreamlike, spectacular closing ceremony as Paris drew curtains on the successful Olympic Games with a stunt-filled event. From Tom Cruise flying through the air from the stadium roof to an exemplary performance by Grammy winner Billie Eilish, the ultimate sporting event came to an end with style.  The 2028 Olympic Games will be held in Los Angeles, following which it will be handed over to Australia.  Latest Blogs\"}"